              </div>
              <div class="input-field col s12 m6">
                <select>
                  <option value="no">没有</option>
                  <option value="little">轻度</option>
                  <option value="middle">中度</option>
                  <option value="large">重度</option>
                </select>
                <label>你是否认为生存没有价值，或者生不如死？</label>
              </div>


              <div class="col s12">
                <button class="right btn waves-effect waves-light yellow black-text" type="submit" name="action">提交
